  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "1. Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Octa-SPI and Quad-SPI are supported for SAIL domain boot",
        "OSPI NOR flash devices run with DDR up to 166 MHz",
        "QSPI NOR flash devices run with SDR up to 83 MHz"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-6-32.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-6-32.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "It is mandatory to contact QTI for the Preferred Vendor List (PVL) validation if the customer plans to use NOR flash devices which are not listed in below:"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-50-24.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-50-24.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2. Schematic diagram for OSPI"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-23_17-43-34.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-23_17-43-34.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-23_17-44-14.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-23_17-44-14.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "3. SPI NorFlash Info"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SPI NorFlash info log print by HY, detail info can refer below:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "[SPINOR] Device ID = 0x3c84c2 [SPINOR] Device Memory density = 2048   Mb [SPINOR] Mode of Operation: DDR_8_8_8( Double Data Rate ) [SPINOR] Frequency of operation = 166 MHz [SPINOR] Frequency of operation = 166 MHz [SPINOR] Device block count = 65536 [SPINOR] Device pages per block = 16 [SPINOR] Device page size in bytes = 256"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SNOR memory size = block count *(pages/per_block pagesize)=65536* (16 *256)=256MB"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-13-54.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-13-54.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "4. Configuration"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Mem Configuration (for NOR 256MB, Number of Sectors is 65536 , for 32MB NOR Number of Sectors is 8192 )"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-24-54.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-24-54.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-25-55.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-25-55.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "MemAcc Configuration"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MemAcc configurate the AddressArea and SubAddressArea."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20configure%20SAIL%20NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-28-36.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/How to configure SAIL NorFlash/image-2024-10-28_19-28-36.png"
    },
